summary: This is a technical log file from CyberLink Power2Go software, detailing the process of copying a disc to an image file and then burning that image to multiple CD-R discs. The log contains system information and burn parameters but no substantive content related to the Epstein case.

events.title: Disc Copy and Burn Process
events.description: A user copied a disc to an image file and then burned that image to multiple CD-R discs using CyberLink Power2Go software.

keyFacts: This document is a technical software log, not a legal or investigative document related to the Epstein case.
The log records a disc copying and burning process that occurred on July 18, 2025.
The file name (EFTA00126217.pdf) suggests it is part of a larger document set, but this specific page contains only technical data.
No names, events, locations, or substantive information related to Jeffrey Epstein or his associates are present in this text.
